MySQL Functions - Realtimeloo ekkadoo kudaa nerchukondi)

1. π—¦π—§π—¥π—π—΅π— π—™π—¨π—΅π—–π—§π—π—Άπ—΅π—¦ (Used in login, search, cleaning user Dataloonu)

 π—™π‚π—»π—°ππ—¶π—Όπ—»                π—π—µπ—®π π—¶π π—±π—Όπ—²π€ (Chudu)      π—¥π—²π—®π—Ή-π—§π—¶π—Ίπ—² Algonex π—¨π€π—²            π—π…π—®π—Ίπ—½π—Ήπ—² 
 CONCAT()             | Join text anthe          | Show full name in UI | SELECT CONCAT(first_name,' ',last_name) FROM users;         
 LOWER()/ UPPER()    | Change case            | Case-insensitive login  | SELECT LOWER(email) FROM users;        
 TRIM()              | Remove spaces          | Clean user input        | SELECT TRIM(name) FROM users;                                 
 SUBSTRING()         | Get part of text       | Mask phone numbers      | SELECT SUBSTRING(phone,1,4) FROM users;                       
 REPLACE()           | Replace text           | Bulk email/domain fix   | SELECT REPLACE(email,'@gmail.com','@company.com') FROM users; 
 INSTR()             | Find position          | Validate email format   | SELECT INSTR(email,'@') FROM users;                           

CONCAT() -> Joins multiple text fields into one
SELECT CONCAT(first_name, ' ', last_name) AS full_name FROM users;
-> Show full names in dashboards, invoices, admin panels(Normalga nuvveppudina job applicationlo fill chesthuntaav kadaa)

LOWER() / UPPER() - Converts text case (Case-insensitive login, email normalization, search)
SELECT LOWER(email) FROM users;

TRIM() - Removes extra spaces(Clean form inputs before storing/searching)
UPDATE users SET name = TRIM(name);

Imp: SUBSTRING()- Extracts part of text (Masking phone/email in UI)
SELECT CONCAT(SUBSTRING(phone,1,2), '******', SUBSTRING(phone,-2)) AS masked FROM users;

REPLACE() - Replaces text patterns(Bulk data cleanup, migrations)
UPDATE users SET email = REPLACE(email, '@gmail.com', '@company.com');

INSTR() - Finds position of substring (Validate email format in quick audits)
SELECT email FROM users WHERE INSTR(email,'@') = 0;

2. π—΅π‚π—Ίπ—²π—Ώπ—¶π—° π—™π‚π—»π—°ππ—¶π—Όπ—»π€ (π—•π—¶π—Ήπ—Ήπ—¶π—»π—΄, π—¥π—²π—½π—Όπ—Ώππ€, π—™π—¶π—»π—®π—»π—°π—²) 

 π—™π‚π—»π—°ππ—¶π—Όπ—»          π—π—µπ—®π π—¶π π—±π—Όπ—²π€)       π—¥π—²π—®π—Ή-π—§π—¶π—Ίπ—² Algonex π—¨π€π—²            π—π…π—®π—Ίπ—½π—Ήπ—² 
 ROUND()            | Round decimals | Currency display         | SELECT ROUND(amount,2) FROM transactions;
CEIL() / FLOOR()    | Round up/down  | Billing rules            | SELECT CEIL(discount) FROM offers;`        
 ABS()              | Make positive  | Balance handling         | SELECT ABS(balance) FROM wallet;`          
 MOD()              | Remainder      | Sharding/partition logic | SELECT MOD(user_id,4) FROM users;`         

ROUND()
3.π——π—®ππ—² & π—§π—¶π—Ίπ—² (π—”π—°ππ—¶πƒπ—¶ππ†, π—§π—Ώπ—¶π—®π—Ήπ€, π—¥π—²π—½π—Όπ—Ώππ€ koam)

 π—™π‚π—»π—°ππ—¶π—Όπ—»          π—π—µπ—®π π—¶π π—±π—Όπ—²π€ teluskoo       π—¥π—²π—®π—Ή-π—§π—¶π—Ίπ—² Algonex π—¨π€π—²            π—π…π—®π—Ίπ—½π—Ήπ—² 
NOW()           | Current date-time       | Store event time  | INSERT INTO logs(ts) VALUES (NOW());                  
CURDATE()       | Todayβ€™s date       | Daily reports     | SELECT CURDATE();                                       
DATEDIFF()      | Days between dates     | Inactive users    | SELECT DATEDIFF(NOW(), last_login) FROM users;         
TIMESTAMPDIFF() | Diff in units          | Trial expiry      | SELECT TIMESTAMPDIFF(DAY, start_at, NOW()) FROM trials; 
DATE_FORMAT()   | Format date            | UI-friendly dates | SELECT DATE_FORMAT(created_at,'%d-%m-%Y') FROM users;   

4. π—”π—΄π—΄π—Ώπ—²π—΄π—®ππ—²π€ (π——π—®π€π—µπ—―π—Όπ—®π—Ώπ—±π€, π—”π—»π—®π—Ήπ†ππ—¶π—°π€ki ani cheppukunnam kadaa) -KPIs, revenue, performance metrics kanukkoniki

 π—™π‚π—»π—°ππ—¶π—Όπ—»          π—π—µπ—®π π—¶π π—±π—Όπ—²π€ teluskoo       π—¥π—²π—®π—Ή-π—§π—¶π—Ίπ—² Algonex π—¨π€π—²            π—π…π—®π—Ίπ—½π—Ήπ—² 
COUNT()         | Count rows   | Total users  | SELECT COUNT(*) FROM users;           
SUM()           | Total amount | Revenue      | SELECT SUM(amount) FROM transactions;
AVG()           | Average      | Ratings      | SELECT AVG(rating) FROM reviews;      
MIN()/ MAX()   | Extremes     | Highest sale | SELECT MAX(amount) FROM transactions;

SELECT COUNT(*) AS users, SUM(amount) AS revenue FROM transactions WHERE created_at >= CURDATE();
Idi Freshers Mistakje: Using COUNT(column) when column can be NULL ->  wrong counts

5. π—–π—Όπ—»π—±π—¶ππ—¶π—Όπ—»π—®π—Ή (π—•π‚π€π—¶π—»π—²π€π€ π—¥π‚π—Ήπ—²π€ π—¶π—» π—¦π—¤π—)

 π—™π‚π—»π—°ππ—¶π—Όπ—»          π—π—µπ—®π π—¶π π—±π—Όπ—²π€ teluskoo       π—¥π—²π—®π—Ή-π—§π—¶π—Ίπ—² Algonex π—¨π€π—²            π—π…π—®π—Ίπ—½π—Ήπ—² 
 IF()     | Simple condition    | Status label       | SELECT IF(balance>0,'Active','Blocked') FROM wallet;                                        
CASE     | Multiple conditions | Risk/grade buckets | SELECT CASE WHEN score>=80 THEN 'High' WHEN score>=50 THEN 'Medium' ELSE 'Low' END FROM users;
IFNULL() | Replace NULL        | Prevent UI crashes | SELECT IFNULL(middle_name,'N/A') FROM users;                                                   

IF() - Simple flags in admin dashboards (Kinda example chudu words ardam kakapothe)
SELECT IF(balance > 0, 'Active', 'Blocked') AS status FROM wallet;

CASE - Segmentation antee ekkuva valuesni seperate cheyandanniki 
SELECT 
CASE 
  WHEN spend >= 100000 THEN 'VIP'
  WHEN spend >= 20000 THEN 'Gold'
  ELSE 'Regular'
END AS segment
FROM customers;

IFNULL() - Prevent UI crashes on NULLs(Letting NULL bubble into frontend)
SELECT IFNULL(profile_pic_url, 'default.png') FROM users;

6. Type Conversion (ETL, APIs, Reports) - Freshers generalga inni functions focus cheyaru but you do 

 π—™π‚π—»π—°ππ—¶π—Όπ—»  π—π—µπ—®π π—¶π π—±π—Όπ—²π€ teluskoo    π—¥π—²π—®π—Ή-π—§π—¶π—Ίπ—² Algonex π—¨π€π—²            π—π…π—®π—Ίπ—½π—Ήπ—² 
CAST()    | Change type         | API compatibility | SELECT CAST(price AS DECIMAL(10,2)) FROM products;
CONVERT() | Change type         | Reporting tools   | SELECT CONVERT(created_at, DATE) FROM users;

CAST() / CONVERT() - Fix API mismatches, reporting toolslo vadatham
SELECT CAST(price AS DECIMAL(10,2)) FROM products;
-> Mixing strings/numbers causing report errors

